gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 106, Rockets 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Rockets, 106-95. Stephen Curry led all scorers with 24 points, seven rebounds, and six assists for the Warriors, while Klay Thompson added 19 points and four rebounds in the victory. Jalen Green tallied 21 points and nine rebounds for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 0-3.
